      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――VENUSプログラムランキング五位との",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the live battle with the 5th ranked team",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ライブバトル終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "in the VENUS program",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.6733331442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、勝ったで！\nうちら、トップ5に勝ったんや！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ we won!\nWe beat a top 5 group!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6524135583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.0116323868
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "今回は、ほんまに頑張ったんよ\n新曲作りもギリギリまで粘ってこだわって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We really worked hard this time.\nWe kept working on the new song until the very last minute…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1999999206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けも、瑠依ちゃんに頼らないフォーメーションを\nみんなで考えて、毎日動けなくなるまで練習して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We came up with a formation that doesn’t rely on Rui-chan…\nWe brainstormed it together and practiced every day until we couldn’t move…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8333332539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.0468928415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ほんまに……ほんまに頑張ったんよ……\n努力が報われるって、こんなに嬉しいものなんや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We really‚ really worked hard…\nI’m so happy that our hard work paid off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.9999999206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.5664623339
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それは優が本気で頑張ったからさ\n頑張った分だけ、報われた時の喜びは増すんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's because you really put your heart into it‚ Yu.\nThe harder you work‚ the greater the joy when it pays off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3999999206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "今までのライブバトルは、勝てそうな相手ばかりで\n心のどこかで余裕があったんやろうなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In our previous live battles‚ our opponents all felt beatable…\nSo somewhere in my heart I had room to spare.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.0333332539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.2531290768
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "せやからこんなに必死になって\nギリギリまで自分を追い込んだりしなかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I never\nPushed myself to the limit like this until the very end…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7333332539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "持てる力を出し尽くして勝つことが、こんなに大変で\nこんなに嬉しいことやったなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never knew that winning by giving it your all could be this hard…\nAnd this happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9666665872,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}